JOHANNESBURG , February 12 -LRB- Xinhua -RRB- -- Lesotho King Letsie III Thursday hailed the close relationship between his kingdom and China , saying there is a bright future for bilateral economic and trade cooperation .
When receiving credentials from Chinese ambassador Chen Laiyuan in Maseru , the king also spoke highly of China 's efforts in maintaining world peace and stability , a report reaching here said Thursday .
He thanked China for its work in safeguarding the interests of developing countries in the United Nations .
Chen , who arrived in Maseru at the end of last year , pledged to try his best to push the existing friendly relations between the two countries to a higher level .
